OL,3,CRape suspect tells court DNA internet
OL,4,Csearches a 'complete coincidence'
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports' Zoe Muldoon was
OL,7,Fin court as Paul Quinn gave evidence
OL,8,Ffor a second day.
OL,10,FA man accused of a brutal rape for
OL,11,Fwhich an innocent man spent 17 years
OL,12,Fin jail told a jury it was a "complete
OL,13,Fcoincidence" he began internet
OL,14,Fsearches following news of a DNA
OL,15,Fbreakthrough in the case.
OL,17,FPaul Quinn, 51, looked up how long DNA
OL,18,Fis kept by police shortly after news
OL,19,Fbroke that police had found forensic
OL,20,Fevidence of a previously unknown
OL,21,Fsuspect for the rape.
