OL,3,CRape suspect tells court DNA internet
OL,4,Csearches a 'complete coincidence'
OL,6,FAnother man, Andrew Malkinson, had
OL,7,Fbeen wrongly picked out at an identity
OL,8,Fparade, convicted and jailed for the
OL,9,Fattack, a "terrible miscarriage of
OL,10,Fjustice", Manchester Crown Court heard.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, prosecutors say the real
OL,13,Fculprit, Quinn, had "feared a knock on
OL,14,Fthe door" as advances in testing
OL,15,Feventually came back with a billion-to-
OL,16,Fone match of his DNA profile left on
OL,17,Fthe victim.
OL,26,@qD@KOUrD@HO]uD@UOUvD@IO]
