OL,3,CRape suspect tells court DNA internet
OL,4,Csearches a 'complete coincidence'
OL,6,FFather-of-six Quinn denies any
OL,7,Finvolvement in the attack on 19 July
OL,8,F2003 on Cleggs Lane, Little Hulton,
OL,9,FSalford.
OL,11,FThe court previously heard Quinn was
OL,12,Faccused of trying to explain away DNA
OL,13,Fevidence by claiming to have been
OL,14,F'very promiscuous' at the time of the
OL,15,Fattack in 2003, telling officers that
OL,16,Fhe'd slept with 'hundreds of women'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
