FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774789868
OL,3,CRape suspect tells court DNA internet
OL,4,Csearches a 'complete coincidence'
OL,6,FQuinn told jurors he was ashamed of
OL,7,Fhis behaviour back then and questioned
OL,8,Fby the prosecutor if he would have
OL,9,Fbeen ashamed and regretful if he'd
OL,10,Fraped a woman, he said: "If I
OL,11,Fcommitted this offence I wouldn't have
OL,12,Fbeen able to live with myself".
OL,14,FJohn Price KC, prosecuting, said in
OL,15,FAugust 2022 news broke about the
OL,16,Fevidence recovered from the vest top
OL,17,Fof the victim.
OL,26,@rD@YOUtD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
