CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774789868
OL,3,CRape suspect tells court DNA internet
OL,4,Csearches a 'complete coincidence'
OL,6,FMr Price told the jury shortly after,
OL,7,FQuinn, who by then had moved from
OL,8,FLittle Hulton to live in Exeter,
OL,9,FDevon, made searches on his iPhone,
OL,10,Fquestioning how long DNA samples are
OL,11,Fkept by police and answers as to why
OL,12,Fhe had begun sweating so much.
OL,14,FMr Price, who said some searches were
OL,15,Fdone late at night, then asked Quinn,
OL,16,Fsat in the witness box: "Did it keep
OL,17,Fyou awake? Couldn't you sleep? Were
OL,18,Fyou feeling anxious at the time? Were
OL,19,Fyou worried?"
OL,21,F"No," the defendant replied.
OL,26,@xD@YOU{D@MO]}D@AOU}D@EO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774789868
OL,3,CRape suspect tells court DNA internet
OL,4,Csearches a 'complete coincidence'
OL,6,FMr Price said: "And you were
OL,7,Ffrightened if they had that DNA on the
OL,8,Fdatabase still, it would come up with
OL,9,Fa match for yours ` which is what
OL,10,Fhappened?"
OL,12,F"No," replied Quinn again, who said
OL,13,Fhis internet searching was because he
OL,14,Fwas "inquisitive" after his DNA had
OL,15,Fbeen taken by police in 2012 and he
OL,16,Fhad an interest in true crime TV
OL,17,Fprogrammes.
OL,26,@nD@POUrD@JO]tD@AOUtD@EO]vD@EOUvD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
