OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774789868
OL,3,CRape suspect tells court DNA internet
OL,4,Csearches a 'complete coincidence'
OL,6,FMr Price continued: "So, is it then, a
OL,7,Fcoincidence, you did this so shortly
OL,8,Fafter the existence of DNA in the
OL,9,FMalkinson case, became public?"
OL,11,F"Complete coincidence," Quinn replied.
OL,13,F"The truth, isn't it Mr Quinn," the
OL,14,Fprosecutor continued, "by the late
OL,15,Fsummer and autumn of 2022, you feared
OL,16,Fthe police would be knocking on your
OL,17,Fdoor?"
OL,19,F"Not at all," Quinn replied, "That
OL,20,Fdidn't interest me."
OL,26,@nD@UOUqD@_O]sD@AOUsD@WO]uD@AOUuD@_O]vD@
OL,26,AWOUyD@FO]{D@AOU{D@MO]{D@^OU|D@TO]
