PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774789868
OL,3,CRape suspect tells court DNA internet
OL,4,Csearches a 'complete coincidence'
OL,6,FMr Price said the evidence showed from
OL,7,Ftime to time Quinn had looked up on
OL,8,Fthe internet developments in the case.
OL,10,FMr Malkinson had made multiple appeals
OL,11,Ffor authorities to review his case
OL,12,Fbefore his final attempt led to his
OL,13,Fappeal against his conviction being
OL,14,Fgranted by the Court of Appeal.
OL,16,FNow aged 60, and originally from
OL,17,FGrimsby, Lincolnshire, he was released
OL,18,Ffrom jail in 2020.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
