PN,39509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774789868
OL,3,CRape suspect tells court DNA internet
OL,4,Csearches a 'complete coincidence'
OL,6,FMr Price, concluding his cross-
OL,7,Fexamination, said: "Then Mr Quinn,
OL,8,Fthere came the day I suggest, when you
OL,9,Flearned of the new DNA evidence and
OL,10,Fyou started to sweat?"
OL,12,F"No, I have always been a hot-blooded
OL,13,Fperson," the defendant said.
OL,15,FMr Price added: "It's you who did it.
OL,16,FAnd that's why your DNA is on her vest
OL,17,Ftop, part of which was bitten by you."
OL,19,F"Not at all," Quinn replied.
OL,26,@oD@TOUrD@VO]tD@AOUuD@HO]wD@QOUyD@fO]{D@
OL,26,AAOU{D@MO]
