OL,3,CRape suspect tells court DNA internet
OL,4,Csearches a 'complete coincidence'
OL,6,FQuinn has pleaded not guilty to two
OL,7,Fcounts of rape, two alternative counts
OL,8,Fof indecent assault, grievous bodily
OL,9,Fharm and attempting to choke or
OL,10,Fstrangle his victim to render her
OL,11,Funconscious while he carried out the
OL,12,Fattack.
OL,14,FThe trial was adjourned until Tuesday
OL,15,Fnext week.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
